// > literally unmangled   expr   => (expr)
// > literally unmangled ((expr)) => (expr)
// 
// `literally just` + `literally unmangled` = `literally as is`
// 
// > literally as is   expr   => expr
// > literally as is ((expr)) => expr
// 
// Also, mangling is not done on identifiers inserted using `$$(...)`, so assuming:
